songs.title: Lak Da Hulara
songs.lyrics:
[Hook]
Sohniye tere lak da hulara, sajna nu maar gya ni
Sun heeriye tere lak da hulara

[Verse 1]
Sajna nu maar gya, gavandiyan nu saarh gya
Vairiyan to jitt gya, par tere agge haar gya
Akhiyan te teriye main sab kujh vaar gya
Rabb 'tay chadeya hun aar gya yaa paar gya
Jado da tere naa leya, odo da ni main saanh leya
Loki mainu kehnde dekho inne kuj khaa leya
Rahwan ch main teriye sab kuj vichata
Mann jaa soniye saara jagg main mana leya
Parr tu ni manni
Lakk jiwe Lamborghini
Zulfa Louis Vuitton di, akhan Fendi
Sohniye de dand jiwe heere-moti
Ve kudi jiwe FAS to import kiti
Soniye da, lakk jiwe Lamborghini
Zulfa Louis Vuitton di, akhan Fendi
Sohniye de, dand jiwe heere-moti
Bayi kudi jiwe Fashion TV vicho kaddi hundi, Inni

[Hook (x2)]
Sohniye tere lak da hulara, sajna nu maar gya ni
Sun heeriye tere lak da hulara

[Verse 2]
Yeah
Meri dua sada hasdi de dand ginna tere
Bayi ja jake le lve ve jihde naal tu fere
Khafa ni main kise nu sata ke kadi khush hoya
Ni te kde kise nu hasa ke kde khud roya ni main
Raati flight ch soya ni main
Sada teri yaadan ch khoya jiwe
Aje vi teri yaadan di hawawan ch uda mera jahaz nhio land hoya jiwe

[Bridge (x4)]
Kyu! mujhe pyar mein dhokha
Kyu! tujhe kisne roka
Main! main tere pyaar mein bhukha
Pyaasa paas tu aja zara sa
